VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://<your-project>.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_<fill-in>

# Note on Wompi: the client never reads the public key from env. The
# wompi-create-order Edge Function returns it in the API response, so all
# three Wompi secrets (public, integrity, events) live in Supabase function
# env only — see supabase/functions/wompi-create-order/index.ts:46.

# The booking drawer always collects a WhatsApp number alongside email. The
# actual WhatsApp delivery is still gated server-side by the WHATSAPP_ENABLED
# secret on the wompi-webhook Edge Function so Minga can turn off paid sends
# without redeploying the apps.
